headline: Arista Networks Rebounds From Key Level After Hiking Sales Outlook, Analyst Day
summary: Arista Networks hit an all-time high of 156.32 on Sept. 11 amid its analyst day before dropping 9% the following day.  Shares of Arista are rebounding from their 21-day moving average now and heading for a weekly gain of more than 5%.  For the third quarter, Arista projected sales of $2.25 billion at the midpoint, slightly above views of $2.12 billion.
